{"tid":1975680,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黃店晚餐  牛油果沙律、卡邦尼意粉","createTime":"2020-04-16T16:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T19:28:53.000Z","uid":62277,"like":102,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"0a1d99ecc486850f54d24fcab055f847e670d05b","tid":1975680,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"本身對呢間cafe無乜期望,就腳入去試下<br />\n覺得都算係有心機整<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛油果沙律用料唔差,開胃<br />\n有香脆既合桃,令配搭無咁單調<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VotVuai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVotVuai.jpg&h=806ff6df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MgpQ2xc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMgpQ2xc.jpg&h=341ef8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkzxwqS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkzxwqS.jpg&h=a7870a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾十蚊一碟意料唔期望有西餐手打意粉質素<br />\n都係港式啲既風格<br />\n但佢至少都做到軟硬適中<br />\n入味得黎唔會碟底成灘汁好濕咁<br />\n意粉似係有炒過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y9q1pNu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy9q1pNu.jpg&h=c3c984a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出面食個港式西餐都過百<br />\n感覺呢度好似更化算"},{"pid":"e52b3deed72ca387d0f1ae64d2d736f9eb613a3c","tid":1975680,"uid":283912,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:58:18.000Z","msg":"牛油果花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地址please<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2387f565e7e10f0b33bbfed0294825c60a62bc93","tid":1975680,"uid":199401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b989bdb71a42fc6054f139584adc946f33443e2c","tid":1975680,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply